data.description: This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-full bath, 2-car screened in garage, POOL HOME, is perfect in so many ways. From the fully remodeled primary bath (2024), updated Kitchen with Stainless Steel appliances, new counter, new backsplash (2021), with a pass-thru into the enclosed heated and air-conditioned lanai with the perfect view of the inground pool, expansive brick paver patio with parking area for a boat or RV(2023) and still large enough for all your outside entertaining, and fully fenced back yard. Exterior of home freshly painted (2023), interior freshly painted (2024). 2 new electrical panels installed with whole house surge protector (2021). New French doors in living room (2021). New sliding door and windows in lanai (2023). These are just a few, of many, of the upgrades that the sellers have made.  The sellers are also offering a 1 year 2-10 Supreme Home Warranty. This home is move-in ready and won't last long. Don't miss out on this great opportunity to own a piece of paradise.
